          <p class="contact-text">
            I'm currently available for full-time roles, contract work, and AI collaboration projects.
            If you're looking for a dedicated developer who can deliver results, let's talk.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:desiertomonchingb@gmail.com" class="contact-cta">
